OL,3,CTearful interview of woman accused of
OL,4,Cmurdering husband played to court
OL,6,FThe tearful first interviews of
OL,7,FChristine Rawle, the woman accused of
OL,8,Fmurdering her husband in North Devon,
OL,9,Fhave been played to a jury.
OL,11,FChristine Rawle, 70, is on trial for
OL,12,Fallegedly stabbing Ian Rawle in the
OL,13,Fback with a large knife at their north
OL,14,FDevon home in 2022. She denies murder.
OL,16,FAt Exeter Crown Court on Wednesday 13
OL,17,FMarch, the jury began hearing the
OL,18,Ffirst of the police interviews with
OL,19,FChristine Rawle that began the day
OL,20,Fafter her husband died.
