OL,3,CTearful interview of woman accused of
OL,4,Cmurdering husband played to court
OL,6,FAsked what had happened that
OL,7,Fafternoon, initially, she told
OL,8,Fdetectives she "just snapped" but then
OL,9,Fsaid the events were like a dream
OL,10,Fafter she had called her husband to
OL,11,Fhelp her with the horses.
OL,13,FShe said: "He said that I was going to
OL,14,Fdie. It just seemed like a bad dream,
OL,15,FI was so afraid, I thought he really
OL,16,Fis going to kill me. He had several
OL,17,Fgoes at it before and I thought this
OL,18,Fis it. And then I don't really
OL,19,Fremember."
