OL,3,CTearful interview of woman accused of
OL,4,Cmurdering husband played to court
OL,6,FIn one she said: "I will see you dead
OL,7,Fbefore I give in, I'll not submit to
OL,8,Fyour torture."
OL,10,FThere were few responses to these from
OL,11,FMr Rawle, but in one he said: "How
OL,12,Fmuch do you expect me to endure."
OL,14,FThe court was also told of a financial
OL,15,Finvestigation into the couple's bank
OL,16,Faccounts and about Mr Rawle's will in
OL,17,Fwhich he had left everything to his
OL,18,Fwife.
