OL,6,FThe jury heard that Mrs Rawle had
OL,7,F"unfettered" access to the couple's
OL,8,Fjoint account, into which all of Mr
OL,9,FRawle's income was paid.
OL,11,FChristine Rawle denies murder. The
OL,12,Ftrial continues.
